eer/\" class=\"hdrNav-mega-menu-cnts-list__item-link\">中途採用</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"hdrNav-mega-menu-cnts-list__item\"><a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pamphlet_20250604.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"hdrNav-mega-menu-cnts-list__item-btn\"><img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/rcnt/images/icon_download.png\" width=\"13\" height=\"14\" class=\"mr10\" alt=\"\">会社案内パンフレット</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- /.hdrNav-mega-menu-cnts -->\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- /.hdrNav-mega-menu -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<!-- /.hdrNav-mega-menu-wrap --></li>\n\t</ul>\n</nav>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"hdr-contact pc\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/contact/\" class=\"hdr-contact__link\" onmousedown=\"gtag('event', 'click', {'event_category': 'お問い合わせフォーム','event_label': 'PC上部リンクボタン'});\">お問い合わせ</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</nav>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</header>\n\n\t\t\n<main class=\"mct\" role=\"main\">\n\n\t\n\t\t\t<header class=\"pageHeader-primary -recruit\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"pageHeader-title inview\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"title\">採用情報</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"slug\">recruit</span>\t\t\t</h1>\n\t\t</header>\n\n\t\n\n\n\t<div class=\"widthBase\">\t<div class=\"breadcrumb\" itemprop=\"breadcrumb\">\n\t\t<!-- Breadcrumb NavXT 7.0.1 -->\n<span property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"HOME（広島精研工業株式会社）\" href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp\" class=\"home\" ><span property=\"name\">HOME<span class=\"pc\">（広島精研工業株式会社）</span></span></a><meta property=\"position\" content=\"1\"></span> &gt; <span property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><span property=\"name\" class=\"archive taxonomy category current-item\">採用情報</span><meta property=\"url\" content=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/recruit/\"><meta property=\"position\" content=\"2\"></span>\t</div>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"both\"></div></div>\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2336\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-2336\" class=\"post-2336 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2336\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2336\">採用情報</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t<nav>\r\n<div class=\"hd_anchor\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-2334\">求める人財</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-2332\">数字で見る広島精研工業</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-2330\">先輩インタビュー</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-2328\">福利厚生制度</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-4181\">認証・登録</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-2326\">募集要項・エントリー</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href=\"#\" data-anchor=\"post-4028\">会社案内パンフレット</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</nav>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2334\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-2334\" class=\"post-2334 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2334\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2334\">求める人財</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t    <div class=\"center\">\r\n      <p class=\"bold f24 f20_sp recruit-top-message\">当社では『夢』を持ち、<br class=\"tab\">その実現に『挑戦』する<br class=\"tab_und\">チャレンジ精神を持ち<br class=\"\">それを『スピード』を持って達成できる人財を<br class=\"sp\">求めています。</p>\r\n      <p class=\"recruit-message mt40 mt20_sp line_h_2\">戦後の日本は大きな急成長を遂げました。<br>\r\n        その原動力となったものは・・・・・・、<br class=\"sp\"><span class=\"bold f24  f20_sp txt_navy\">やはり『人』</span><br>\r\n        人はお互いが支えあって何かを形成していきます。<br>\r\n        家族、会社、地域、国、良くするのも悪くするのも人。<br>\r\n        広島精研工業株式会社では、これまで培ってきた風土や技術力を<br class=\"pc\">\r\n        さらに向上させていくことに力を発揮できる人を求めます。</p>\r\n    </div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2332\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-2332\" class=\"post-2332 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2332\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2332\">数字で見る広島精研工業</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box__num\">\r\n      <div> <img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/icon_founded.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n        <p class=\"f24  f16_sp mt10\">創業</p>\r\n        <div class=\"box_wht\"><span>\r\n          <p class=\"f24  f16_sp\">1951年創業</p>\r\n          </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div> <img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/icon_employee.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n        <p class=\"f24  f16_sp mt10\">従業員数</p>\r\n        <div class=\"box_wht\"><span>\r\n          <p class=\"f24  f16_sp\">194名</p>\r\n          </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div> <img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/icon_ratio.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n        <p class=\"f24  f16_sp mt10\">男女比率</p>\r\n        <div class=\"box_wht\"><span>\r\n          <p class=\"f20 f12_sp\">男性123名：女性71名</p>\r\n          </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div> <img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/icon_calendar.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n        <p class=\"f24  f16_sp mt10\">年間休日</p>\r\n        <div class=\"box_wht\"><span>\r\n          <p class=\"f24  f16_sp\">118日</p>\r\n          </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div> <img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/icon_holiday.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n        <p class=\"f24  f16_sp mt10\">平均有給休暇取得日数</p>\r\n        <div class=\"box_wht\"><span>\r\n          <p class=\"f24  f16_sp\">10.8日</p>\r\n          </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div> <img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/icon_service.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n        <p class=\"f24  f16_sp mt10\">平均勤続年数</p>\r\n        <div class=\"box_wht\"><span>\r\n          <p class=\"f24  f16_sp\">9.5年</p>\r\n          </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2330\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-2330\" class=\"post-2330 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2330\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2330\">先輩インタビュー</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"nav__interview\">\r\n    <div> <a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/recruit/interview/?anchor-id=sec01\">\r\n    <div>\r\n        <p class=\"f22 f14_sp bold\">製造部<br>\r\n        製造1課</p>\r\n        <p class=\"txt_grn\">2019年入社</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div>\r\n        <figure><img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/pic_staff_01.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </a> </div>\r\n    <div> <a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/recruit/interview/?anchor-id=sec02\">\r\n    <div>\r\n        <p class=\"f22 f14_sp bold\">技術部<br>\r\n        車体・塗装技術課</p>\r\n        <p class=\"txt_grn\">2022年入社</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div>\r\n        <figure><img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/pic_staff_04.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </a> </div>\r\n    <div> <a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/recruit/interview/?anchor-id=sec04\">\r\n    <div>\r\n        <p class=\"f22 f14_sp bold\">営業部<br>\r\n        営業・購買 Gr</p>\r\n        <p class=\"txt_grn\">2019年入社</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div>\r\n        <figure><img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/pic_staff_03-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </a> </div>\r\n</div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2328\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-2328\" class=\"post-2328 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2328\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2328\">福利厚生制度</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"center line_h_2\">当社は次世代育成支援対策推進法に基づき「一般事業主行動計画」を策定し、<br class=\"pc\" />\r\n従業員の仕事と子育てや介護の両立支援をする企業を目指しています。<br class=\"tab_hide\" />\r\n社員は育児や介護休業に関して「会社の就業規則」に準じて、女性社員だけでなく、男性社員も同様に取得できます。</p>\r\n<table class=\"tbl_fukuri\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>各種手当</th>\r\n<td>家族手当、通勤手当、時間外勤務等</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>休暇</th>\r\n<td>年次有給休暇　慶弔休暇　特別休暇　産前産後休暇　育児休暇　介護休暇</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>福利厚生</th>\r\n<td>雇用、労災、健康、厚生、退職金制度、資格取得支援制度</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>社内設備</th>\r\n<td>社内で休憩室を手作りし、周辺に自動販売機やウォーターサーバーを設置しています。<br />\r\n夏には、熱中症対策として塩飴や、ソフトドリンクの支給も行っています。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<figure class=\"mt60 mt30_sp center\"><img src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/pic_recruit_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2326-3\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-4181\" class=\"post-4181 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2326-3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2326-3\">認証・登録</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"u-flex u-flex-jcsa u-flex-fdc-s\">\r\n<div class=\"u-flex u-flex-fdc u-flex-aic-s\">\r\n<div>ユースエール認定制度</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/logo_youth_yell_01.png\" width=\"145\" height=\"145\" alt=\"\">\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"center line_h_2 f18 f14_sp u-flex u-flex-aic u-flex-jcc-s mt20_sp\">若者の採用・育成に積極的で、若者の雇用管理の状況などが<br>優良な中小企業を厚生労働大臣が認定する制度です。</p>\r\n</div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2326\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-2326\" class=\"post-2326 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2326\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2326\">募集要項・エントリー</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t    <div class=\"nav_bnr\">\r\n      <div class=\"bnr_grn\"> <a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/recruit/graduate/\">\r\n        <p class=\"mt10 f34 f26_tab\">新卒採用</p>\r\n        <p class=\"f20 f14_sp mt10 list\">募集要項・エントリーはこちら</p>\r\n        </a></div>\r\n      <div class=\"bnr_blue\"> <a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/recruit/mid-career/\">\r\n        <p class=\"mt10 f34 f26_tab\">中途・パート採用</p>\r\n        <p class=\"f20 f14_sp mt10 list\">募集要項・エントリーはこちら</p>\r\n        </a> </div>\r\n    </div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"both30\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- #post-## -->\n\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"post_anchorpoint\" id=\"anchor-2326-2\"></a>\n\t<div id=\"post-4028\" class=\"post-4028 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-recruit\">\n\t\t<div class=\"widthBase postWrap-2326-2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title title-2326-2\">会社案内パンフレット</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pic_pamphlet.jpg\" width=\"360\" height=\"509\"></figure>\r\n<p class=\"sec-recruit__btn mt40\"><a href=\"https://www.h-seiken.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pamphlet_20250604.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-secondary -white\" rel=\"noopener\">パンフレットはこちら</a></p>\t\t\t\t<di